- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also a likely category as the paper uses machine learning methods to classify individual postings to social media. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is another possible category as the paper discusses the appropriate use of machine learning methods in predicting social events. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may touch on issues of privacy and security in using social media data. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is also a less likely category, but possible as the paper may discuss the development and implementation of the Bayesian method for event prediction.
